{"tid":2113515,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：不排除安排確診者及檢疫者須「共存」於鯉魚門公園度假村","createTime":"2020-07-18T07:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T07:51:01.000Z","uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a84e8cc849ce152afc584d7a6fd89832be299485","tid":2113515,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三波疫情嚴峻，對公立醫院構成壓力。《明報》引述消息指，醫管局已選址柴灣鯉魚門公園度假村接收病徵輕微的確診者。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，鯉魚門已停收檢疫者，但由於病情變化迅速，不排除確診者及檢疫者須「共存」，但醫管局會盡量避免兩者混合於同一場合。<br />\n<br />\n鯉魚門將有護士全天候當值，以視像形式巡房。病人須自行量度血壓和體溫，並以平板電腦將資料傳送至控制中心。類近的東區醫院將提供日常起居飲食的支援。<br />\n<br />\n病人每日須作深喉唾液檢測，連續兩日陰性即可出院。鯉魚門亦設有醫療站，病情有變可前往檢查，嚴重者將送往東區醫院。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導（明報）<br />\n<br />\n#香港新聞 #武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/weatherjj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fweatherjj&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiTpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=88513f5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/weatherjj</a>"},{"pid":"e8d4864d71128999756f2124fc4020eb868c3397","tid":2113515,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0e981ea03740e656d4f563fca799eff5ab5fe3","tid":2113515,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b9911f5b067dfb427d9d4bab3222e62044ca8b","tid":2113515,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab8d5a6f8c7ebe7a827be55012b4737e30bde18","tid":2113515,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:51:01.000Z","msg":"做埋愛好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}